                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-56" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;exitX=0;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=1;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" parent="1" source="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-14" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-52" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-57" value="" style="image;aspect=fixed;html=1;points=[];align=center;fontSize=12;image=img/lib/azure2/ai_machine_learning/AI_Studio.svg;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2010" y="821.5" width="32.94" height="35" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-58" value="Raises PR&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;+ enable auto-merge&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1581" y="1190" width="200" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-67" value="Agent Review PR&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;LLM code review via GH API&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1580" y="1277" width="200" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="sec-scans-node" value="Security Agent&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;diff-only triage&lt;br&gt;Sonar + Checkmarx One&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1581" y="1120" width="199" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="sec-scans-loopback" value="critical → fix" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;dashed=1;exitX=0;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.75;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" parent="1" source="sec-scans-node" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-66" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
                        <Array as="points">
                            <mxPoint x="1410" y="1140"/>
                            <mxPoint x="1410" y="1040"/>
                        </Array>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="badge-secscans" value="VERIFY" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=9;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1729.5" y="1126" width="45" height="14" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="sec-agent-note" value="&lt;b&gt;Security Agent &amp;mdash; details&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scope:&lt;/b&gt; diff-only. Pre-existing findings on touched files are ignored to avoid blocking unrelated PRs. Backlog hygiene is handled by scheduled full-repo scans (IMPROVE stage, auto-files JIRA).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sources (consumed via API, not re-run):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 &lt;b&gt;SonarQube&lt;/b&gt; \u2014 PR analysis mode; Quality Gate &quot;on New Code&quot;.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 &lt;b&gt;Checkmarx One&lt;/b&gt; \u2014 filter findings to &lt;i&gt;status=New&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Decision:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 &lt;b&gt;critical&lt;/b&gt; \u2192 loop back to Generate Code with structured fix proposal (dismisses stale approvals).&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 &lt;b&gt;high / medium / low&lt;/b&gt; \u2192 post as PR comments; do not block.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Notes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 The scanners themselves still run as required CI status checks on the PR (branch-protection gate). The agent is the triage + auto-fix layer on top.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 Scanners are licensed/audited tools \u2014 we do not replace them with the LLM. The LLM only triages and proposes fixes.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\u2022 Sysdig (image / runtime / IaC) is intentionally out of scope here; it gates the deploy pipeline downstream, not the source PR." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff8dc;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="520" y="667" width="500" height="333" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-68" value="Await GH Webhook&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;merged | abandoned | changes_requested&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=0;dashed=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1580" y="1400" width="200" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-69" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;" parent="1" source="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-58" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-67" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-70" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;" parent="1" source="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-67" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-68" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-71" value="merged | abandoned" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;" parent="1" source="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-68" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-43" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-72" value="" style="endArrow=block;html=1;rounded=0;dashed=1;exitX=0;exitY=0.5;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;entryX=0;entryY=0.5;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;" parent="1" source="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-68" target="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-66" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry">
                        <Array as="points">
                            <mxPoint x="1480" y="1270"/>
                            <mxPoint x="1480" y="1020"/>
                        </Array>
                    </mxGeometry>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="EdAH23wTT8TAoaTBZzOQ-73" value="&lt;b&gt;PR Lifecycle (Read Execution → Raises PR → Agent Review → Auto-merge)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1. Read Execution&lt;/b&gt;: pod completes, posts callback {branch, head_sha, files_changed} to control plane. Pod exits.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2. Raises PR&lt;/b&gt;: control plane opens PR (base=main, head=feature/AOS-XX) using GitHub App #1 (author). Body rendered from ticket + plan + clarifications. Immediately enables &lt;i&gt;auto-merge&lt;/i&gt; (squash) — GH holds it armed and merges atomically once all branch-protection gates are green.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3a. Agent Review PR (code review)&lt;/b&gt;: control plane fetches diff via GH API, calls LLM with ticket + plan + diff. Posts a formal review via GitHub App #2 (reviewer): APPROVE or REQUEST_CHANGES.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3b. Security Agent (diff-only)&lt;/b&gt;: triages findings from Sonar PR analysis + Checkmarx One (filter status=New). On critical → loops back to Generate Code with a fix proposal. Otherwise posts comments and proceeds. See &quot;Security Agent—details&quot; side note.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;4. Await GH Webhook&lt;/b&gt;: graph suspends. Branch protection requires N approvals (1 bot + 1 human) + CI green + conversations resolved. Human reviews directly on GitHub.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Terminal events (pull_request webhook):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• closed, merged=true → post_merge: JIRA Done, status=completed&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• closed, merged=false → abandon: JIRA Won&#39;t Do, status=cancelled&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;• review changes_requested → re-dispatch Generate Code with feedback (same branch, dismisses stale approvals)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff8dc;strokeColor=#999999;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=8;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2770" y="960" width="260" height="570" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
